query:
UPDATE trip_routes 
SET name = 'Liptovský Mikuláš → Demänovská Ice Cave',
    mapData = NULL
WHERE tripId = 30001 AND id = (
  SELECT id FROM trip_routes 
  WHERE tripId = 30001 
  ORDER BY id 
  LIMIT 1 OFFSET 4
);
